=\"color: red;\">飲酒對心血管疾病、第2型糖尿病有益</span>，可以每天少量喝一些。<br />\n<br />\n至於檳榔會引發口腔癌，且吃得愈頻繁，嚼的時間愈長，頰、舌部位癌變的比例明顯增加，發病年齡也比其他癌症患者平均提早8年左右。<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171119/bkncn-20171119041113831-1119_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171119%2Fbkncn-20171119041113831-1119_05011_001.html&d=xUcJZgEr%2B061WxnRHYnldKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=560d2c99\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171119/bkncn-20171119041113831-1119_05011_001.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得出呢個結果嘅研究唔係randomised controlled trial，而只係分析subjects飲酒習慣同佢地嘅健康狀況。唔飲酒嘅subjects之中有部分係戒咗酒，戒酒原因有部分係因為健康出現問題，以致呢一組嘅健康差啲。所以少量飲酒係咪可以減少心血管疾病其實仲係controversial<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05791d02f8cfa658a2eeb4c934ed783307d63d19","tid":473218,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:08:15.000Z","msg":"咁我想問韓國日本都有，嗰D會唔會都係咁"},{"pid":"f2877515c8970d7247b0b07dfe7405264620a9c9","tid":473218,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢老先食<br />\n最好食多啲快撚啲死</blockquote><br />\n講得好<br />\n以夢冇雪櫃就要醃姐<br />\n家陣有新鮮魚唔食食垃圾"},{"pid":"5c0845071d03c61ae759813552f0d906566601a5","tid":473218,"uid":52595,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:21:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3083d79b039352ffe19da3f2a97a227f66c76f28","tid":473218,"uid":107212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:22:41.000Z","msg":"鹹蛋整法係咪都類似？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58142bd93f16d2963c1ab00f79e3a28c8c80d8a2","tid":473218,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"無人叫你日日食<br />\n<br />\n不過都係 可以就戒左佢囉<br />\n火腿 餐肉 咸魚 腸仔"},{"pid":"ad21b024ecae8d3fc24fc89c18cdc309dc4c11e1","tid":473218,"uid":19261,"like":23,"dislike":18,"score":5,"citedBy